        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The “Direct Finance Scheme by NSFDC (GSCDC)” scheme was launched by the Social Justice and Empowerment Department, Government of Gujarat. The scheme aims to provide concessional credit facilities to Scheduled Caste persons for self-employment opportunities. Under this scheme, loans are provided at subsidized rates of interest ranging from 1% to 5%, enabling beneficiaries to start their own income-generating ventures.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- Provide a loan for self-employment to a scheduled caste person at a low interest rate of just 1% to 5%.\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "Under this scheme, loans are offered at a low interest rate, ranging from 1% to 5%, specifically for self-employment to scheduled caste (SC) individuals. ",
