          "process_md": "> **Registration Process:**\n\n\n- Visit the Gujarat Scheduled Caste Development Corporation, Gandhinagar [official website](https://gscdconline.gujarat.gov.in/Account/ApplicationLogin). - Click on the &quot;New user (Register)&quot;.\n- Fill the registration form:  Email ID, Mobile Number, Password for login, Confirm Password.\n- Click on the &quot;Submit.\n- After successful registration, User ID and Password will be generated.\n\n> **Login and Application Process:**\n\n\n- Enter User Name, Password, and Captcha Code.\n\n\n- After login, schemes applicable to your caste will be displayed.\n- Click on the scheme you want to apply for.\n- Fill out the &quot;Application Form&quot; and upload the required documents\n- Click Save Application. The system will generate an Application Number.\n- Click Print Application.\n\n<br>\n\n"
        }
